node.text:
Thanks for all your kindness to us Aussies. Please visit us. We can’t wait to see you 🧡

Repost: @australia ❤️
We want to send our mates around the world a big thank you for all your love and support. We hope you will come visit soon!

node.text:
Snuggles on our sunset tour 🌅😍
#Repost @emiliede_ravin  My last night in Alice Spings was no question the most special! I’ve been dreaming of visiting @thekangaroosanctuary for ages…Omg. The place is magical. Brolga- you are one of the kindest most caring, loving & nurturing humans I’ve ever met. These little joeys & Roos are so lucky to have you as their “Kangaroo Mum” 🥰 Thank you so much for sharing your beautiful stories with me & educating me on what to do if I find a baby Joey. Was an experience of a lifetime 🥰. 
P.S. if you live in Australia - always check a road kill Roo’s pouch ‘cos most of the time the joeys survive, for days sometimes. And carry a pillow case in your car to put the Joey in. If it’s TEENY tiny with no hair, put it under your shirt on your skin so it is warm. (Then go to the closest vet) Xoxox🦘❤️🇦🇺
